#MIPEA - 2017-03-06- US X3-11264 ST X3-25377- START
Call C_CPY(VALEUR) From SUBHRFRM
#Call C_CPY(VALEUR) From SUBFRM
#MIPEA - 2017-03-06- US X3-11264 ST X3-25377- END
